##보증서

yellow-06 이 제작한 카드뉴스 뷰어 소프트웨어에는 다음 오픈소스 소프트웨어가 사용되었음.
==========================================================================================
1. AlertDialog
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/app/AlertDialog.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

2. Dialog
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/app/Dialog.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

3. DialogInterface
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/content/DialogInterface.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

4. Intent
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/content/Intent.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

5. Bundle
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/os/Bundle.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

6. View
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/view/View.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

7. Button
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/widget/Button.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

8. Toast
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/widget/Toast.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

9. LayoutInFlater
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/view/LayoutInflater.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

10. ViewGroup
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/view/ViewGroup.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

11. BaseAdapter
https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/base/+/master/core/java/android/widget/BaseAdapter.java
라이센스: Apache 2.0

12. ImageView
